&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.6304&amp;fp-y=0.5012&amp;h=1333&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=aaebc7740cefc3647af373c4830cd8c4 2000w"
