            <figcaption class="attribution">
                <span class="attribution__caption">We’re interested in any barriers you faced to getting your car back and whether the tow company followed the required steps. <a href="https://www.propublica.org/getinvolved/car-towing-connecticut-help-propublica-investigate">Share your experiences with us here.</a> 

</span>     <span class="attribution__credit">Anuj Shrestha, special to ProPublica</span>
            </figcaption>
        </li>
       
        
    </ul>
