<div class="lead-in">
            <p class="lead-in__title" id="has-your-car-been-towed-in-connecticut-share-your-story-and-help-us-investigate">Has Your Car Been Towed in Connecticut? Share Your Story and Help Us Investigate.</p>
                <div class="lead-in__intro">
            <p>We’re investigating towing practices in Connecticut, where companies can sell people’s cars after just 15 days. If you’ve been affected, we want to hear from you.</p>

        </div>
    </div>


