        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/getinvolved/car-towing-connecticut-help-propublica-investigate">
                                    Has Your Car Been Towed in Connecticut? Share Your Story and Help Us Investigate.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            We’re investigating towing practices in Connecticut, where companies can sell people’s cars after just 15 days. If you’ve been affected, we want to hear from you.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://ctmirror.org/author/gmonk/">Ginny Monk</a>, <a class="name" href="https://ctmirror.org/author/daltimari/">Dave Altimari</a> and <a class="name" href="https://ctmirror.org/author/srasekh/">Shahrzad Rasekh</a>, <a href="https://ctmirror.org/">The Connecticut Mirror</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-01-05EST05:05">Jan. 5, 5:05 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

