    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/inside-secret-ap3-militia-american-patriots-three-percent">
                                    Armed and Underground: Inside the Turbulent, Secret World of an American Militia
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Rounding up migrants. Lists of “friendly” sheriffs. Debating political assassinations. Internal messages reveal AP3’s journey from Jan. 6 through the tumultuous lead-up to the 2024 election. One member predicts: “It’ll be decided at the ammo box.”
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/joshua-kaplan">Joshua Kaplan</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-08-17EDT06:00">Aug. 17, 2024, 6 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

